  "prompt": "Where is the best guitar buying shop in Guwahati?",
  "response": "Guwahati, as a major city in Assam, has several music stores where you can purchase guitars. Some of the well-regarded places include:\n\n1. **Musical Emporium**: Located in Paltan Bazaar, it's known for a wide range of musical instruments, including guitars, both acoustic and electric.\n\n2. **Bharat Musical Mart**: Also in Paltan Bazaar, this store has been around for many years and offers a variety of guitars and other musical instruments.\n\n3. **Furtados Music**: Though primarily an online retailer, Furtados Music also has outlets in various cities. It's worth checking if they have a presence in Guwahati or offer delivery services to the area.\n\n4. **Raga Music Shop**: Situated around Fancy Bazaar, this store is another popular choice for buying guitars and other musical equipment.\n\n5. **Sounds & Strings**: Located in Christian Basti, they are known for their collection of guitars and other musical instruments.\n\nIt's always a good idea to check online reviews, visit the stores to see their collection, and consult with store staff to find the best guitar that fits your needs and budget.",
